---
import Layout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-800">Case Videos</h1>

        <div class="space-y-8">
            <!-- Wells Fargo Case -->
            <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">
                    Wells Fargo Sales Misconduct and Culture
                </h2>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <span
                        class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >
                        3 sources
                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        The provided sources primarily consist of excerpts from
                        a Harvard Business Review case study concerning Sales
                        Misconduct at Wells Fargo Community Bank, along with a
                        very brief mention of conflicts of interest from a
                        separate document titled "integrity.pdf." The extensive
                        Wells Fargo case details the timeline and fallout of the
                        unauthorized account scandal from 2011 to 2016, where
                        employees opened millions of "ghost accounts" due to
                        aggressive sales pressure and unrealistic quotas. It
                        outlines the bank's response, including executive
                        terminations, clawbacks, and attempts to centralize risk
                        management following regulatory settlements. The text
                        also summarizes the recommendations of proxy advisors,
                        Glass Lewis and Institutional Shareholders Services
                        (ISS), ahead of the 2017 annual shareholder meeting
                        regarding the re-election of the Board of Directors.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="video-container">
                    <div style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto;">
                        <div
                            style="position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;"
                        >
                            <iframe
                                src="https://hbs.sharepoint.com/sites/sectionj2027leadership/_layouts/15/embed.aspx?UniqueId=ff1bb8d7-375e-4877-b840-614d014a37cc&embed=%7B%22hvm%22%3Atrue%2C%22ust%22%3Atrue%7D&referrer=OneUpFileViewer&referrerScenario=EmbedDialog.Create"
                                width="1280"
                                height="720"
                                frameborder="0"
                                scrolling="no"
                                allowfullscreen
                                title="wells-fargo"
                                style="border:none; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; height: 100%; max-width: 100%;"
                            >
                            </iframe>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Placeholder for more videos -->
            <div class="text-center py-8">
                <p class="text-gray-500 italic">
                    More case videos will be added soon...
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
